Set in a lightweight stainless steel carabiner, it attaches quickly and securely to key rings, jackets-just about anything with a hook or zipper. Its long-lasting LED bulb provides an ambient glow bright enough for everything from reading fine print to finding your car door keyhole. Choose from two modes: press once for steady glow, twice for continuous flash. The SpotLit is water-resistant, and long-life, replaceable lithium batteries are included. The SpotLit is now available in colorful, eye-catching Pink, Orange, and Lime Green plastic powered by a bright white LED. The result is a fun & functional new option that still provides the high quality LED illumination you love about the SpotLit. Product Features Push button switch Operates on and includes 2 coin cell 2016 3v lithium batteries that have a 20 hour run time in glow mode Available in white plastic with red white blue green or disco-multicolored LED bulbs New color options include pink lime green or orange plastic with white LED bulbs Product dimensions are 2-Inch x 1.25-Inch x .75-Inch

Condition : This item is brand new, unopened and sealed in its original factory box.
